Step 1: Start
Step 2: Initialize File System
Step 4: Set All Files as Unallocated
Step 5: Repeat Steps Till User Chooses to Exit. Then go to Step 10
Step 6: Enter File Starting Block and Length
Step 7: Check Blocks from Starting Block to Length is Unallocated
Step 8: If Yes, Allocate the File, Display Allocated and go to Step 6.
Step 9: Else Display File Cannot be Allocated and go to Step 6
Step 10: Stop